</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Goku's Ultra Instinct Walk</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After attaining his newest transformation, Goku sets his sights on Jiren, casually disregarding anything attempting to interfere in his walk towards him. Jiren recognizes this trope, and calls off his second in command, allowing him to fight Goku one on one. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Slow Walk</span> </h3>
</div>
<div class="square_ad footer-article-ad main_2" data-isolated="0"></div>
